                <h3>REVOLVING (PRE-FINANCE)</h3>
                <p>GOLD is a cash back commodity, and Mining is a capital-intensive venture. As such, the only way to secure regular supply at reasonable and realistic discounts is to Pre-Finance.</p>
                <p>This arrangement allows clients consistent supply of GOLD at good discount. Clients are required to make monthly orders for a minimum of 6 months. Supply commences 14 days – 30 days after full</p>
                <p>payment is received. The advantage is to have good reasonable discount and thereby increasing profit and satisfaction for our clients. This is 100% Pre-finance.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="column">
                <img src="../Assets/images/pexels-linkedin-sales-navigator-2182977.jpg" alt="">
                <h3>JOINT VENTURE</h3>
                <p>This arrangement is there to address the insatiable desire of the investor who loves to partner a growing business. There is room for flexibility, safety, confidence,</p>
                <p>satisfaction, transparency and above all maximization of return on investment. The terms are negotiable in this particular</p>
                <p>aspect that exploits the rich concessions available and under the management of TAAKIN PRECIOUS METAL</p>
            </article>
            <article class="column">
                <img src="../Assets/images/19gold4.jpg" alt="">
                <h3>GOLD DEALINGS</h3>
                <p>TAAKIN PRECIOUS METAL is licensed to Purchase Gold from SMALL SCALE MINING Companies in Ghana. This opportunity puts TAAKIN PRECIOUS METAL in a pole position to access Gold regularly when it is mined.</p>
                <p>Clients are implored to open a Metal Account with TAAKIN PRECIOUS METAL for Gold Dealing.</p>
                <p>With this account in place, Clients have an option to deposit funds into their Metal Account for ready Purchase once Gold is available. The advantage here is to have replicable access to Gold to be purchased to meet Clients’ requests.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="column">
                <img src="../Assets/images/gold-altin.jpg" alt="">
