                <p>TAAKIN PRECIOUS METAL which is licensed by the Minerals Commission of Ghana, exports Gold from Accra, Ghana to any destination/refinery of the client through Emirates Sky Cargo or KLM, Royal Dutch</p>
                <p>Airlines as mandated by the conditions in the License. Clients across the Globe can comfortably place an order and make payment for Export Services of Gold purchased from 3rd Parties through TAAKIN PRECIOUS METAL without travelling to Accra .</p>
